Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個……謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.71,0:03:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒完
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.39,0:03:43.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萊拉 支援我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:03:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是導師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然無效嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:13.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並非無效
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.58,0:04:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是它的污穢太強烈了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真讓人看不下去 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扎比達
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.11,0:04:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扎比達……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.40,0:05:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這小子就是新的導師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.03,0:05:15.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那是你幹的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憑魔由我來送下地獄 這就是我的做派
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他擁有能夠消滅憑魔的特殊道具與道具要使用的子彈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.98,0:05:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這玩意兒是特製的 是我特別特別重要的搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把殺害當成做派……？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定還有可以不取性命就能救它的方法啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.37,0:05:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可真高尚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.90,0:05:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管哪個時代的導師都是一群好學生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.23,0:05:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過啊 導師大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.51,0:05:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也說不定……有的人是只有殺了他才算是救他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.19,0:06:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這話什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.05,0:06:03.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那個……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:07.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扎比達
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我應該跟你說過別再來這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也應該跟你說過 艾德娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.79,0:06:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管多少次我都會來 直到殺了他為止
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就……別再管我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:33.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這難道是領域？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.55,0:06:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼充滿污穢的……是領域？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:41.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.32,0:07:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.01,0:07:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道……怎麼會……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.69,0:07:26.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 這條龍就是艾德娜的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.18,0:07:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾森
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們幾個！不想被吃掉的話就快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.40,0:07:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萊拉！我們趕快「神依」！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這原本是天族的話 就用淨化的力量來……！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:45.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行！史雷！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢貨！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.29,0:07:55.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實體化的龍是沒法淨化的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:07:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那……艾德娜的哥哥不就……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.76,0:08:05.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠……都是這個樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.86,0:08:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的……沒有辦法能解決嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:11.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方法我去找過 然而無計可施
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 所以我得親手 送他下地獄！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾德娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.74,0:08:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就別管我哥哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.75,0:08:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷！這裡太危險了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.24,0:08:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:43.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊帶艾德娜跑遠點兒！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.47,0:08:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.82,0:09:03.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和之前的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.49,0:09:26.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憑魔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有淨化的力量還是沒法打倒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 在這種地方……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.36,0:09:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷不能沒我陪著……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.60,0:10:18.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事了 他好像飛遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.57,0:10:22.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算抓我的手抓到什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.59,0:10:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.57,0:10:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是乎 你們的目的是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.18,0:10:35.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要來這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:38.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是依循龍的傳說來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要屠龍劍聖的稱號嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.38,0:10:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 艾德娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.23,0:10:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實是在瑞迪雷克有龍出現……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.15,0:10:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首都有龍？那不是我哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.81,0:10:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.00,0:10:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你來幹嘛的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在這個被稱作「災厄的時代」的世界是什麼樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果說龍是毀滅的象徵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.40,0:11:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那追尋龍的蹤跡 說不定就能更瞭解世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.05,0:11:20.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我成為了導師 所以……必須要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.56,0:11:26.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 那你現在知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.19,0:11:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍到底是個什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.13,0:11:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你再待在這裡也是白費功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.36,0:11:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以趕緊回……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:36.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 關於龍我已經清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:45.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我在想 要救龍……要救艾森應該怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萊拉 這小子是不是傻？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷的優點就是特別直率啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.03,0:11:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 一群笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:08.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾德娜 艾森為什麼會變成龍？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.24,0:12:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.59,0:12:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也不說一聲就離開 再見到就已經變成龍了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:21.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是個很喜歡人類的怪胎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.74,0:12:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是因為他跟人走得太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在尋找讓哥哥恢復原樣的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.07,0:12:35.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是無濟於事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.51,0:12:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪兒都沒有能淨化龍的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.54,0:12:44.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:47.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:49.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能殺掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.06,0:12:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是……你並不希望他被殺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.57,0:12:58.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才你也想阻止扎比達來著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.16,0:13:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前一直以為導師和龍都是傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.29,0:13:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來真的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這世界上還有好多沒有被揭開過的傳說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定會有拯救龍的方法……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.59,0:13:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那是……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:13:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾森……扎比達……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.97,0:13:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扎比達！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.94,0:14:15.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們幾個 不許再靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.34,0:14:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙已經不是艾森了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他都不知道站在那邊的是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已經忘記一切了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘了我們之前打過多少次架
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.23,0:14:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘了他曾經拼上性命旅行過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.46,0:14:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘了跟我一起喝到酩酊大醉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.95,0:14:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些你全都……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾森！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.14,0:14:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萊拉 請助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:47.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍是無法淨化的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.83,0:14:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我……想做點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我必須去做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.25,0:15:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷 已經……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒……我還能……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.62,0:17:09.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.06,0:17:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.86,0:17:19.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再傷害別人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.45,0:17:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾德娜 快離開那裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.55,0:17:26.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥……哥……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.17,0:18:09.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾森 你……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.56,0:18:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扎比達
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.41,0:18:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扎比達 那個……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.61,0:18:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 你想說艾森是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.96,0:18:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟看見了那一幕……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.05,0:18:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扎比達……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.01,0:18:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過啊 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.29,0:18:54.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也滿世界轉過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:19:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但從來沒聽說過龍能恢復原樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.50,0:19:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 世界那麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.19,0:19:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒準……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.76,0:19:13.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去找找也沒什麼不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.66,0:19:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.49,0:19:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾德娜 你什麼時候打算放棄他 隨時來跟我說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.38,0:19:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會立刻飛奔過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.30,0:19:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟早就跟他約好了……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.29,0:19:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總算有一個笨蛋走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.93,0:19:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾德娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.76,0:19:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萊拉 麻煩你進行陪神契約
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.72,0:19:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾多娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:54.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陪神？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是遵循古時的契約 我借給你力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.02,0:20:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說要救艾森 所以我要幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.03,0:20:11.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是答應要幫我找拯救哥哥的辦法嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 肯定幫你 我們一起找！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.29,0:20:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多指教了 史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.98,0:20:33.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也請你多指教 艾德娜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.34,0:22:10.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你等著 史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.60,0:22:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.79,0:22:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.11,0:22:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.17,0:22:27.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格裡弗雷特橋被……
